description: '''Jayden Yen Dumont''' (born February 24, 2006) known professionally as '''Jaydes''' (previously known as '''Evvls'''), is an American rapper, singer, producer, and songwriter from [[Tamarac, Florida]]. He gained popularity in the [[Underground hip hop|underground hip-hop]] scene in 2022 from [[social media]] and [[Music streaming service|streaming platforms]] such as [[SoundCloud]]. His most popular song is Rose, that gained virality on [[TikTok]].
